criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Patient ≥ 18 years old

          -  Patient with information form signed to participate in the study;

          -  Patient presenting a cancer with bone metastases at the level of the proximal femur
             and having a Y-STRUT® medical device implanted;

          -  Patient able to complete a questionnaire.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Patient who refuse to participate to this study;

          -  Patient already enrolled in a clinical study, excluding his participation to
             HIPPON100.
